lead_paragraph: Travis Wood got four outs and made an impressive catch in left field. Pitcher Jon Lester made the winning play — at the plate. Five Chicago Cubs played two or more positions.

headline.print_headline: Lester Squeezes in Deciding Run, Cubs Beat Mariners in 12
